>Description:
A nice, easy way to get SirMail to lock into an error box loop (i.e., you hit OK and the error box pops up again, forever)
>How-To-Repeat:
Start sirmail.
Hit ALT-F by accident, looking for a keystroke for followup
Press hide on the find bar
Loop forever
